rows.label: tlk43500147_02_msg0001
rows.name:
That bloke Cole-san at Bajena Playhouse
is really a master of his craft.

rows.label: tlk43500147_02_msg0002
rows.name:
But there's something a bit suspicious
about him...

rows.label: tlk43500147_02_msg0003
rows.name:
He's always got that hood up. Hard
to tell if he's even really an Invidian.

rows.label: tlk43500147_02_msg0004
rows.name: I hear he used to be a mercenary too.

rows.label: tlk43500147_02_msg0005
rows.name:
I can't imagine how he
wound up in showbiz...
